bnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F201130_009ab9b5332cc1cdff518dca095b5740.jpg&h=5f4277d3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係肝氣鬱結，舌暗代表你身體入面有啲瘀血，<br />\n調理吓會有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 臭脾氣，好炆憎，經前胸脹，經色紫暗，月經有血塊等都係比較典型既症狀</blockquote><br />\n中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝郎中指點<br />\n其實有睇過中醫 啲藥粉真係好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長期戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034a49e80ab153ec9e8ecfdede8eea324260c547","tid":245644,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來咁多EQ低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為係家教問題</blockquote><br />\n的確係家教問題<br />\n身邊父母係高學歷既朋友脾氣都好好<br />\n佢地父母成日同佢地深度對談<br />\n我有時都會去取下經 通常聽完佢地講野 嗰排就會好上進+豁達<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過我朋友就話日日食晚飯都聽佢老竇講野會癲</span>"},{"pid":"9f531072c36836e42e5f0ad69f3d5237d3923458","tid":245644,"uid":107774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來咁多EQ低能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為係家教問題</blockquote><br />\n的確係家教問題<br />\n身邊父母係高學歷既朋友脾氣都好好<br />\n佢地父母成日同佢地深度對談<br />\n我有時都會去取下經 通常聽完佢地講野 嗰排就會好上進+豁達<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過我朋友就話日日食晚飯都聽佢老竇講野會癲</span></blockquote><br />\n咁賴老豆老母都得？我老豆老母都係低學歷 又唔見我似你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}